30 min of actively going offense and actually doing damage a good amount of that time and you figure I woulda had someone by then, but no I never actually got anyone under 90, nor did the other bard.  It wasnt until they all left down to 1 necro who was trying to just channel through us that we actually got someone under 80, we actually got him to 70 after about 30 sec of trying to wear him down while he just tanked everything (he wasnt trying to lifetap) and he just evac'd to zone in and left us chillin there.<br>
<br>
