<br>
If you have not PvP'd much in group PvP, without really sounding elitist, you really do not know much about things.<br>
<br>
The crux is, MOBILITY is the key in PvP, and since mobility affecting debufs are almost impossible to land on players with high end resists, without a team debuff effort, selo is the only reliable way to go faster than the opposition.<br>
<br>
It comes down to this.<br>
<br>
Take a group made by any combination of classes without a bard.<br>
<br>
Take a group made exactly with the above group, but add a bard and remove anyone person.<br>
<br>
The second group will always win.  Heck, if a bard did NOTHING but grant Selo to all the people in his group, they'd still be incredibly sought after PvP.<br>
<br>
Why is speed so important?<br>
<br>
- Jousting.  The person with the highest speed decides when the joust happens.<br>
<br>
- Your casters can get spells off, your melees can get on their casters to interrupt, and not vice versa.<br>
<br>
- You can pull off in case of low health to run for a heal, you cannot 'run away' if you go slower than the person chasing you.<br>
<br>
I really encourage anyone to try some group PvP - it is honestly enormous fun, good tactics, and perhaps some of the most skill intensive stuff you can do <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jimmayjam>Jimmay Jam</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 405<br> <font color=#330000>(7/1/04 1:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19557.topic&index=14>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://userpic.livejournal.com/3740691/162948 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> K now take a bard by himself, and what is the argument? Take your time on this one if you need to ok? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mearisthecowslayer>Mearis The Cowslayer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 140<br> <font color=#330000>(7/1/04 1:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19557.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> I'd reply to that one but Liq would have to lock the thread <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--